&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;The Assembly &amp;amp; Test Technician is responsible for executing pressure testing, mechanical assembly, precision cleaning, and thermal insulation work.&amp;nbsp; You will work alongside leadership and engineering to conduct pressure testing, mechanical assembly, and precision cleaning work on various fluid assemblies for the Terran R rocket and Aeon R rocket engine.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
